fulltitle: Philip Agee Predicts the Rise of Far-Right Leaders like Donald Trump in 1992
title: Philip Agee Predicts the Rise of Far-Right Leaders like Donald Trump in 1992
_filename: _Philip Agee Predicts the Rise of Far-Right Leaders like Donald Trump in 1992.mp4
description:
FULL TALK: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=197Op8BMAwE Agee predicts the rise of the far-right in Europe and the USA due to the failures of neo-liberal capitalism. He speaks specifically about the 1990s militia movement, plus a combination of klansmen, christian fundamentalist, extremist libertarians, and neo-nazis. These are the groups that have made of some of the coalition supporting the candidacy of Donald Trump in the United States.

Philip Agee was a long-time CIA officer in Central and South America. He became disaffected with the methods and goals of the CIA, and blew the whistle in a book about the CIA called 'Inside the Company'.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
